Al Ain, Abu Dhabi
MEP Supervisor
Location: Al Ain, UAE
JOB ROLE
Oversee planning, design and implementation of MEP services for government plant or facility expansion projects of our client. Interaction with technical consultants to ensure design of MEP services is as per clients requirements. Based on experience appropriate technologies to be suggested to reduce operational costs Check Bill of Quantities of all services against drawings submitted by the consultants Identify vendors for supply of MEP equipment Identify contractors for carrying out MEP work on site Procurement of all material and ensuring timely delivery on site Ability to manage men, material and site progress Supervise work & monitor as per construction drawings & documents
KEY AREAS OF RESPONSIBILITY
Planning, design and implementation of MEP services for government projects Interaction with consultants during design stage Interaction with vendors during procurement stage Interaction with contractors during construction stage Verification of actual construction work with services drawings
QUALIFICATIONS
Bachelor’s degree in Mechanical/Electrical Engineering
EXPERIENCE REQUIRED
10 years of MEP Experience
Job Type: Contract Duration: 7-8 Months Salary: 35000- 40000 AED PM Project: Industrial
